### Wrack
- **Skillset:** Physiology
- **ABADMIN ID:** 28
- **Syntax:**
  - `WRACK <target> <humour|affliction>`
- **Works on/against:** Adventurers and denizens
- **Cooldown / lane:** 2.00 seconds of balance
- **Resource:** 60 mana
- **Type:** Humour conversion / damage-or-affliction
- **Notes:**
  - Assaults an opponent's humours to cause damage or afflictions.
  - Each humour has several afflictions and one associated damage type.
  - If no affliction is specified, one may manifest at random at a slight speed penalty.
